          </a>
         </div>
        </div>
        <h3>
         <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GZVmqBTyXBE" target="_blank">
          Video: Stuart Altman, Sol C. Chaikin Professor of National Health Policy and Chair of Massachusetts' Health Policy Commission, discusses the Heller School's historical influence on U.S. health systems.
         </a>
        </h3>
       </div>
